tags: I just don't know whether to laugh cry or BOTH
summary: Okay, so me and my friends had our Secret Santa today, and my friend Xavier got me; so I was kinda shocked to see two presents,...
caption:
Okay, so me and my friends had our Secret Santa today, and my friend Xavier got me; so I was kinda shocked to see two presents, instead of just one. So, I open the smaller bag, and I just saw the top of the glass vase in the picture…until I pull it out of the back, see the black sand in it that looks like ashes, and I immediately put the pieces together.

“Oh, you mother-!”

He started to laugh and then said he ‘picked something else up in Wakanda for (me)’. I opened the bigger bag and was presented with this! v

It’s Bucky’s Wakandan-made arm, and I can actually wear it!

Oh, my friend just thinks he’s soooo clever!…which he is, because I started crying, I was laughing too hard. He had been planning this shit since fucking APRIL when Infinity War came out and I sobbed when Bucky died. Bucky’s my favorite, after all.

I appreciate the joke, and I love the gifts, but seriously….

Can’t you see the pain I’m in, here?! XD

body:
Avengers 4 Theory

There are lots of theorys about Antman going back in time using a time vortex while in the quantum realm, but I think they are wrong.

At the end of the Avengers 4 trailer Antman is shown with his van on a recording of a security camera, and in the top left of the screen is what people believe is the date of the recording, which is 1985.

If Antman used a time vortex while in the quantum realm, than how does he have the van with him in 1985?
